    "phase_c_legal_correctness_note": "The AUDIT_PRE_MANUAL_TESTING report flagged Thüringen as a renumbering BLOCKER (claimed current ThürBO 2024 uses §§ 64/65/67 for Bauvorlageberechtigung/Bautechnische Nachweise/Bauantrag). VERIFIED FALSE POSITIVE: the current ThürBO vom 2. Juli 2024 confirms §§ 67/72/74 — exactly this corpus. Cross-confirmed against the official Inhaltsübersicht (landesrecht.thueringen.de jlr-BauOTH2024pIVZ), the current-version text (klimaschutzdigital.de Stand 02.07.2024), and the law's own internal cross-references (§ 68 references the § 67 Liste; § 71 names bauvorlageberechtigte Ingenieure). NO § numbers changed. The official portal returns a JS shell to automated fetch, so tier stays secondary-mirror, but the numbering is cross-confirmed current."
  },
